Package: stimgate
Type: Package
Title: Identify responding cells as outliers
Version: 0.99.1-1
Authors@R: person("Miguel", "Rodo", , "miguel.rodo@uct.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2036-4878"))
Description: Apply outlier gating function to identify cells that have possibly
    responded to stimulation, by comparing the unstimulated and stimulated tubes
    from the same sample.
